column5: My youngest stayed up with me to get things done for the morning.She was determined not to go to sleep, and to fish in the am.Pic1.well I tried to wake her up, she was out cold.I came home and got this after fishing.Pic2.I told her that it was slow and the white stripe kittie was out and I got this,LOLPic3.
Cute pics Vince. I miss the days when my daughters still thought fishing was fun..

Thanks guys!lOL.When I take my to girls out I get skunked!LOL.My youngest as in the pics nailed a 5 lb smally flat linnin in temagami.My oldest last fathers day nailed a 4 lb pickerel in front of fishmasters.Caint wait till this fathers day,out fishin with my girls.I hope I do well,they have the luck.LOL.
